name: Mega Model 1.8 - Mega EVOLVED
description:
Mega Model 1.8 - Mega EVOLVED

(I have updated the 1.4 version to include the 1.8 version)

If you want to make a donation to show appreciation for this model https://ko-fi.com/asmrgaming However the model is free to all

Sitting at 950 Models merged together currently. - this is version 1.8. results are very sharp. Highly detailed semi realistic anime is probably the best description but it does a wide variety of images. Feedback and ideas for 1.9 are more than welcome. For 1.8 you will need to make sure both the safesensor and yaml config file are downloaded and installed in the same directory or you wont get the proper results. this is because of multi language support built into the model based on the alt-diffusion model - mostly for chinesse, french, spanish and a few other language specific models that can work with english and vise versa.

works fine with easy diffusion UI as well - which is the program i use to run it, automatic1111 and stable diffusion WebUI are fine with the config file placed alongside the saftensor - config file will be in a light blue message on the upper right side of this page on the download screen.

Version 1.5 and 1.6 can be found by accessing my username, or searching for mega model.

Credit to all the model makers, merges and the community in general without which this wouldnt be possible. Hope u all enjoy it and feel free to merge it into your own models as well - im interested to see what people do with this

My username is u/ollobrains on reddit if u have any questions u can drop me a line there

modelVersions.name: 1.8 Enhanced
modelVersions.description:
Ok i have taken 10% of the experimental mega model 4.8 (with 1000s of LORA files merged in) and merged it with MM1.8 having a 90% weighting. This side upgrade is the result, and in my opinion it greatly boosts 1.8. So hopefully everyone enjoys this and it shows that using the merged LORA approach can intergrate with older versions and upgrade their capabilities
